-qu%C3%A2n-chi%E1%BA%BFn-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ca/poem-r-0sKzn4t1sF64MC4QGgRg">Thạch tướng quân chiến trường ca - 石將軍戰場歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-QwR8mfkWimm7tarlC84k4w">Lý Mộng Dương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-_JP2zt_WU35ztf0-XnF5WQ">Thuật hoài kỳ 1 - 述懷其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/author-MvAX8pIr0uu6mqdrhe1jhA">Nguyễn Xuân Ôn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Tr%C3%A0o-chi%E1%BA%BFt-t%C3%BD-ph%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-vUxGRNIkDp-YJ_YFNJQSeA">Trào chiết tý phật kỳ 1 - 嘲折臂佛其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/T%C3%B9-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-Zh5cqGL6NScJjOhiT5ffiw">Tù lương - 囚糧</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
